  "keyFeatures": [
    "14-phase scan orchestrator running fully on-device without root",
    "SOCKS5 unauthenticated proxy detection exposing VPN server exit IPs",
    "Clash REST API leak detection revealing all active connections and server IPs",
    "xray gRPC API detection allowing config and key dump",
    "/proc/net/tcp fingerprinting to identify VPN client by listening port patterns",
    "MTU anomaly and DNS private-subnet detection as indirect VPN signals",
    "VPN client identification across 19 known packages (v2rayNG, NekoBox, Hiddify, etc.)",
    "IP geolocation of discovered VPN server addresses",
    "Work Profile and Samsung Knox isolation bypass awareness",
    "Split tunnel detection via direct vs proxy IP comparison"
  ],
